name: Mackenzie Canadian Government Long Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive Canadian Long Term Government Bond Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in Canadian federal and provincial government long dated debt instruments. The Fund seeks to provide longterm capital appreciation.
